To initialize the object in your project you need to import the class module clsTimeAsString.

Then in your procedure, declare the object using early binding:

Dim objVariable As New clsTimeAsString

NOTE: You must use early binding as shown above.

REGULAR EXPRESSIONS: You must have regular expressions turned on in your project workbook. After saving your workbook as an *.xlsm file:

1. Go to VBA editor (Alt + F11)
2. Go to Tools -> References
3. Put a checkmark beside Microsoft VBScript Regular Expressions 5.5" or higher.
4. Click OK and Save your workbook again.
